The paper focuses on image captioning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model integrates attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG) to improve performance. Additionally, the paper mentions the creation of two game datasets, indicating a potential focus on gaming applications (cs.GR). Finally, the use of residual connections in the attention networks suggests a potential focus on deep learning (cs.AI).
